@NODE Background "Warhost Background"

   Warhost is a top-viewed strategic tank command game, based loosely around
a number of commercial and P.D. games, including U.F.O. and Scorched Tanks.
   Demis and I had been talking about this superb strategy game we
wanted to write which would be a combined battlefield strategy and overall
army management game, based in deep space, with you fighting away against all
manner of heinous alien foes with strange tentacled slimey eyes and stuff.
   Then he went back to work for Bullfrog, so we never got round to writing
it.  Instead, I wrote this little game because I wanted to write something
with a nice simple principle and nice straight-forward code, but with a
little bit of an edge.
   Thus Warhost was born.  It may not be much, but the un-registered
version, at least, is worth infinitely more than you have paid for it. =>

@ENDNODE

